# Task: walk

Make the robot walk forward. You must produce exactly **4 Policy objects** that define one complete gait cycle. This cycle will be **looped automatically** for several seconds.

## Reward

- **Pose**: R_pose = -(|Δh| + |Δroll| + |Δpitch|). Stay upright and level.
- **Distance**: R_dist = distance_weight × forward_distance. Move in the +x direction.

Total reward = R_pose + R_dist. Higher is better.

